      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IDEAL FRANKIE (4) carries a big boom into this having easily won her two starts so far. Beat of all these rivals when cruising home by a whopping 47m in the heat of this series, drawing wider but working forward to find the front and clearing out. Draws lower so it is hard to see how they turn the tables. SWEETSUCCESS (2) raced greenly when she debuted with a third in the heats. She was a long way off IDEAL FRANKIE there but she draws lower and may be better for the experience. GRANDIOSA (6) draws wider but chased along the sprint lane to split the top two in the heat. Trifecta hope along with EVERY CENT COUNTS (5) who came from the back row for fourth on debut and is open to natural improvement.",
